headline: Interactive Brokers Group to Present at Piper Sandler Global Exchange & Trading Conference
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., May 29, 2025--Interactive Brokers Group, Inc. (Nasdaq: IBKR) announces that its Chairman Thomas Peterffy will speak at the Piper Sandler Global Exchange & Trading Conference on Thursday, June 5th at 9:30 a.m. ET.
